ITEM NO.36               COURT NO.11               SECTION II-B
               S U P R E M E  C O U R T  O F  I N D I A
                       RECORD OF PROCEEDINGS
Petition(s) for Special Leave to Appeal (Crl.)  No(s).  7749/2025
[Arising out of impugned final judgment and order dated  22-01-2025
in CRLA No. 209/2000 passed by the High Court of Kerala at
Ernakulam]
K C ARISH                                          Petitioner(s)
                                VERSUS
CENTRAL BUREAU OF INVESTIGATION 
SPECIAL POLICE ESTABLISHMENT Respondent(s)
(FOR ADMISSION , IA No. 113014/2025 - EXEMPTION FROM FILING O.T.)
 
Date : 07-07-2025 This matter was called on for hearing today.
CORAM : 
         HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE SUDHANSHU DHULIA
         HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE JOYMALYA BAGCHI
(PARTIAL COURT WORKING DAYS BENCH)
For Petitioner(s)  Mr. Ranjith K. C., AOR
                   
For Respondent(s)  Mr. S.D.Sanjay, A.S.G.
                   Mr. Mukesh Kumar Maroria, AOR
                   Mr. Akshay Amritanshu, Adv.
                   Mr. Madhav Sinhal, Adv.
                   Mr. Anmol Chandan, Adv.
Ms. Nikita Sethi, Adv.
Mr. Khushal Kolwar, Adv.
                   
          UPON hearing the counsel the Court made the following
                             O R D E R
At the request of adjournment made by the learned counsel for
the  petitioner(s),  list  this  matter  in  the  week  commencing
21.07.2025.
Interim order shall extended till the next date of hearing.
(NIRMALA NEGI)                                  (RENU BALA GAMBHIR)
ASTT. REGISTRAR-cum-PS                        ASSISTANT  REGISTRAR
